OL,3,CAds for sunbed firms banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading and irresponsible safety
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FAdverts for five tanning companies
OL,8,Fhave been banned for making misleading
OL,9,Fand irresponsible claims about the
OL,10,Fsafety of sunbeds.
OL,12,FAds for tanning studios The Sun
OL,13,FCompany, SunShine Co and Tanbox
OL,14,FTowcester, as well as for Tan &
OL,15,FDeliver Home Hire Sunbeds and Byrokko,
OL,16,Fwhich sells products to accelerate
OL,17,Ftanning, made "a number of problematic
OL,18,Fclaims" about safety, the Advertising
OL,19,FStandards Authority (ASA) said.
