OL,3,CAds for sunbed firms banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading and irresponsible safety
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FTheir misleading and irresponsible
OL,8,Fclaims included that sunbed use is
OL,9,Fsafe or that tanning can be achieved
OL,10,Fsafely, and that sunbeds could boost
OL,11,Fvitamin D, improve mood and energy
OL,12,Flevels, and treat health conditions
OL,13,Fsuch as seasonal affective disorder
OL,14,F(SAD), psoriasis and eczema.
OL,16,FThe ASA said it found the ads using
OL,17,Fits AI-powered Active Ad Monitoring
OL,18,Fsystem.
