OL,3,CAds for sunbed firms banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading and irresponsible safety
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe watchdog said the rulings come
OL,8,Famid public health concerns about the
OL,9,Frisks of ultraviolet (UV) exposure and
OL,10,Fthe continued popularity of tanning,
OL,11,Fwith some experts highlighting the
OL,12,Frole of social media in promoting and
OL,13,Fnormalising sunbed use.
OL,15,FLong-standing advice from the NHS and
OL,16,FCancer Research UK says there is no
OL,17,Fsafe or healthy way to get a tan using
OL,18,FUV radiation.
