OL,3,CAds for sunbed firms banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading and irresponsible safety
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FCancer Research UK warns that sunbeds
OL,8,Fuse high-intensity UV radiation for
OL,9,Fquick tanning which can damage the DNA
OL,10,Fin skin cells. This can lead to skin
OL,11,Fcancer, including melanoma, which is
OL,12,Fthe most serious type.
OL,14,FToo much UV radiation is the third
OL,15,Fbiggest cause of cancer and the main
OL,16,Fcause of skin cancer in the UK.
