OL,3,CAds for sunbed firms banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading and irresponsible safety
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe ASA said the ads for all five
OL,8,Ffirms were irresponsible and likely to
OL,9,Fmislead people for downplaying the
OL,10,Frisks or presenting tanning as
OL,11,Fbeneficial to health.
OL,13,FSome of the ads also implied that
OL,14,Fsunbeds could be used to help manage
OL,15,Fmedical conditions, which risked
OL,16,Fdiscouraging people from seeking
OL,17,Fappropriate medical advice or
OL,18,Ftreatment, it added.
