OL,3,CAds for sunbed firms banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading and irresponsible safety
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FAll five advertisers have been told
OL,8,Fthe banned ads must not appear again,
OL,9,Fand that future advertising must not
OL,10,Fsuggest that sunbeds are safe, provide
OL,11,Fhealth benefits or can be used to
OL,12,Ftreat medical conditions.
OL,14,FThe ASA's regulatory projects manager,
OL,15,FJess Tye, said: "Given the serious
OL,16,Fdangers of UV exposure, it's vital
OL,17,Fthat ads for sunbeds don't suggest
OL,18,Fthat they're safe or offer health
OL,19,Fbenefits.
