OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"These rulings demonstrate that
OL,8,Finformation about health in ads must
OL,9,Fbe clear, accurate and responsible.
OL,11,F"Protecting people from misleading or
OL,12,Firresponsible ads is at the heart of
OL,13,Four work and we'll take action where
OL,14,Fads break the rules by putting people
OL,15,Fat risk."
OL,17,FAll five firms have been approached
OL,18,Ffor comment.
