OL,7,FThe Sun Company said: "We acknowledge
OL,8,Fthe ASA's ruling in relation to an
OL,9,Fearly social media post made shortly
OL,10,Fafter opening. The specific content
OL,11,Freferenced in the ruling has been
OL,12,Fremoved, and we have reviewed our
OL,13,Fadvertising practices to ensure full
OL,14,Fcompliance going forward.
OL,16,F"Customer transparency and regulatory
OL,17,Fcompliance are important to us."
